#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php includes/class-admin.php:82
#: includes/class-admin.php:83
msgid "Studio317 Report Drafts for Google Analytics"
msgstr "Studio317 Report Drafts for Google Analytics"

#. Description of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php
msgid ""
"Creates AI-assisted report drafts from GA4 data in the WordPress user "
"language with admin review, editing, and copy tools."
msgstr ""
"GA4データから、WordPressユーザー言語に合わせたAI支援のレポート下書きを作成"
"し、管理画面で確認・編集・コピーできます。"

#. Author of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php
msgid "Kimiya Watabe / Studio317"
msgstr "Kimiya Watabe / Studio317"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php
msgid "https://business.s317.com/"
msgstr "https://business.s317.com/"

#: includes/class-admin.php:93 includes/class-admin.php:94
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:68
msgid "Report Builder"
msgstr "レポートビルダー"

#: includes/class-admin.php:102 includes/class-admin.php:103
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:85
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "設定"

#: includes/class-admin.php:142
msgid ""
"Directory scope matches paths that start with the entered path, such as /"
"blog/."
msgstr ""
"ディレクトリ範囲では、/blog/ など入力したパスで始まるページを対象にします。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:143
msgid "Page scope matches the exact normalized path, such as /about."
msgstr "ページ範囲では、/about など正規化された完全一致のパスを対象にします。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:144
msgid "Copied."
msgstr "コピーしました。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:145
msgid "Copy failed. Please select and copy manually."
msgstr "コピーできませんでした。選択して手動でコピーしてください。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:146
msgid "Nothing to copy."
msgstr "コピーする内容がありません。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:183 includes/class-admin.php:276
#: includes/class-admin.php:321
msgid ""
"You do not have permission to manage Studio317 Report Drafts for Google "
"Analytics credentials."
msgstr ""
"Studio317 Report Drafts for Google Analytics の認証情報を管理する権限がありま"
"せん。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:184 includes/class-admin.php:277
#: includes/class-admin.php:322
msgid "Permission denied"
msgstr "権限がありません"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:271
msgid "GA4 Property ID is not configured."
msgstr "GA4プロパティIDが設定されていません。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:278
msgid ""
"No Google connection is available for GA4 Fetch. Connect Google in Settings "
"and try again."
msgstr ""
"GA4データ取得に使用できるGoogle接続がありません。設定でGoogleに接続してから再"
"試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:290
msgid "GA4 report period is invalid."
msgstr "GA4レポート期間が無効です。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:344
msgid ""
"Could not connect to Google Analytics Data API. Check the server network "
"connection and try again."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API に接続できませんでした。サーバーのネットワーク接続"
"を確認して再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:359
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API returned an unreadable response. Please try again "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API から読み取れないレスポンスが返されました。時間をお"
"いて再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:649 includes/class-ga4-client.php:673
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API rejected the report request. Check the GA4 "
"property ID, date range, and report filters."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API がレポートリクエストを拒否しました。GA4プロパティ"
"ID、期間、レポートフィルターを確認してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:653 includes/class-ga4-client.php:677
msgid ""
"Google credential is invalid or expired. Reconnect Google in Settings and "
"try again."
msgstr ""
"Google認証情報が無効または期限切れです。設定でGoogleに再接続してから再試行し"
"てください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:657 includes/class-ga4-client.php:681
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API permission was denied. Check that the token has "
"access to the selected GA4 property."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API の権限が拒否されました。選択したGA4プロパティにトー"
"クンがアクセスできるか確認してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:661 includes/class-ga4-client.php:685
msgid ""
"GA4 property was not found. Check that the property ID is correct and that "
"the token can access it."
msgstr ""
"GA4プロパティが見つかりません。プロパティIDが正しいことと、トークンがアクセス"
"できることを確認してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:665 includes/class-ga4-client.php:689
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API rate limit may have been exceeded. Please wait and "
"try again later."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API のレート制限に達した可能性があります。しばらく待っ"
"てから再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:669 includes/class-ga4-client.php:693
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API is temporarily unavailable. Please try again later."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API は一時的に利用できません。時間をおいて再試行してく"
"ださい。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:696
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API returned an unexpected error. Check the settings "
"and try again."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API から予期しないエラーが返されました。設定を確認して"
"再試行してください。"

#. translators: 1: safe user-facing error message, 2: HTTP status code.
#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:731 includes/class-openai-client.php:215
#, php-format
msgid "%1$s HTTP status: %2$d"
msgstr "%1$s HTTPステータス: %2$d"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:32
msgid ""
"OpenAI API key is not configured. Open Settings and add an API key, or "
"configure it on the server before generating."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI APIキーが設定されていません。生成する前に、設定画面でAPIキーを追加する"
"か、サーバー側で設定してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:62
msgid ""
"Could not connect to OpenAI API. Check the server network connection and try "
"again."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API に接続できませんでした。サーバーのネットワーク接続を確認して再試行"
"してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:77
msgid "OpenAI API returned an unreadable response. Please try again later."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API から読み取れないレスポンスが返されました。時間をおいて再試行してく"
"ださい。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:86
msgid "OpenAI API returned no report text."
msgstr "OpenAI API からレポート本文が返されませんでした。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:131 includes/class-openai-client.php:155
msgid ""
"OpenAI API rejected the request. Check the report data and model "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API がリクエストを拒否しました。レポートデータとモデル設定を確認してく"
"ださい。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:135 includes/class-openai-client.php:159
msgid ""
"OpenAI API authentication failed. Review the configured OpenAI API key "
"without sharing key values."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API の認証に失敗しました。キー値を共有せずに、設定済みのOpenAI APIキー"
"を確認してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:139 includes/class-openai-client.php:166
msgid ""
"OpenAI API permission was denied. If you use a restricted key, allow Model "
"capabilities and Responses (/v1/responses) requests."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API の権限が拒否されました。制限付きキーを使用する場合は、Model "
"capabilities と Responses (/v1/responses) のリクエストを許可してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:143 includes/class-openai-client.php:170
msgid ""
"The configured OpenAI model or endpoint was not found. Check the model "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"設定されたOpenAIモデルまたはエンドポイントが見つかりません。モデル設定を確認"
"してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:147 includes/class-openai-client.php:177
msgid ""
"OpenAI API rate limit or quota may have been exceeded. Check your OpenAI "
"Platform usage and billing."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API のレート制限またはクォータに達した可能性があります。OpenAI "
"Platform の使用状況と請求設定を確認してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:151
msgid "OpenAI API is temporarily unavailable. Please try again later."
msgstr "OpenAI API は一時的に利用できません。時間をおいて再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-openai-client.php:180
msgid ""
"OpenAI API returned an unexpected error. Review the OpenAI configuration and "
"try again without sharing request or response details."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI API から予期しないエラーが返されました。リクエストやレスポンスの詳細を"
"共有せずにOpenAI設定を確認し、再試行してください。"

#. translators: %s: Settings screen link.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:78
#, php-format
msgid "Current setup (configure %s first)"
msgstr "現在の設定状況（はじめに%sしてください）"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:93 includes/class-settings.php:377
msgid "GA4 Property ID"
msgstr "GA4プロパティID"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:99 includes/class-report-builder.php:121
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1413 includes/class-settings.php:786
#: includes/class-settings.php:858
msgid "Not configured"
msgstr "未設定"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:105 includes/class-settings.php:520
msgid "Host Name Filter"
msgstr "ホスト名フィルター"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:108
msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "有効"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:110
msgid "Not in use"
msgstr "未使用"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:115 includes/class-settings.php:539
msgid "Host Name"
msgstr "ホスト名"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:127 includes/class-settings.php:295
msgid "Google connection"
msgstr "Google接続"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:137
msgid ""
"Connect or reconnect Google in Settings before fetching GA4 data. Token "
"values are hidden."
msgstr ""
"GA4データを取得する前に、設定でGoogleに接続または再接続してください。トークン"
"値は非表示です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:142
msgid "OpenAI API key"
msgstr "OpenAI APIキー"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:152
msgid ""
"Configure an OpenAI API key in Settings before generating an AI report "
"draft. Key values are hidden."
msgstr ""
"AIレポート下書きを生成する前に、設定でOpenAI APIキーを設定してください。キー"
"値は非表示です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:157
msgid "Report language"
msgstr "レポート言語"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:161
msgid ""
"The report draft language is resolved from the current WordPress user "
"language, then the site language, then English. The WordPress timezone is "
"not used to choose the report language."
msgstr ""
"レポート下書きの言語は、現在のWordPressユーザー言語、サイト言語、英語の順で決"
"定されます。WordPressのタイムゾーンはレポート言語の判定には使用されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:169
msgid ""
"This screen uses a two-step flow: fetch GA4 data first, review the Data "
"Preview, then generate a report draft in the current WordPress user language "
"with OpenAI."
msgstr ""
"この画面では、まずGA4データを取得し、送信データのプレビューを確認してから、"
"OpenAIで現在のWordPressユーザー言語に合わせたレポート下書きを生成します。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:177
msgid "Report Conditions"
msgstr "レポート条件"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:183 includes/class-report-builder.php:933
msgid "Date Range"
msgstr "期間"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:187
msgid "Start Date"
msgstr "開始日"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:197
msgid "End Date"
msgstr "終了日"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:207
msgid ""
"The default date range is the previous month based on the WordPress timezone."
msgstr "デフォルトの期間は、WordPressのタイムゾーンに基づく前月です。"

#. translators: %d: maximum number of report days.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:214
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The report period is limited to %d days to keep GA4 requests and report data "
"manageable."
msgstr ""
"GA4リクエストとレポートデータを扱いやすく保つため、レポート期間は%d日までに制"
"限されています。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:224 includes/class-report-builder.php:229
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:941 includes/class-report-builder.php:1434
msgid "Comparison"
msgstr "比較"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:246
msgid ""
"When comparison is enabled, the selected period is shifted to the previous "
"month or previous year and fetched separately from GA4."
msgstr ""
"比較を有効にすると、選択期間を前月または前年にずらした期間をGA4から別途取得し"
"ます。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:253 includes/class-report-builder.php:258
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:957
msgid "Data Scope"
msgstr "データ範囲"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:277
msgid "Path"
msgstr "パス"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:291
msgid ""
"For directory scope, enter a path such as /blog/. For page scope, enter a "
"path such as /about."
msgstr ""
"ディレクトリ範囲では /blog/ のようなパスを入力します。ページ範囲では /about "
"のようなパスを入力します。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:296
msgid ""
"Site scope covers all paths. Directory scope matches paths that start with "
"the entered path. Page scope matches the exact normalized path. Full URLs "
"are not allowed."
msgstr ""
"サイト全体はすべてのパスを対象にします。ディレクトリ範囲は入力したパスで始ま"
"るパスに一致し、ページ範囲は正規化されたパスに完全一致します。完全なURLは使用"
"できません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:304
msgid "Data sent to Google Analytics Data API"
msgstr "Google Analytics Data API に送信されるデータ"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:307
msgid ""
"When you click Fetch GA4 Data, the selected date range, comparison setting, "
"data scope, host name/path filters, and required metrics/dimensions are sent "
"to the Google Analytics Data API."
msgstr ""
"「GA4データを取得」をクリックすると、選択した期間、比較設定、データ範囲、ホス"
"ト名・パスのフィルター、必要な指標とディメンションが Google Analytics Data "
"API に送信されます。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:312
msgid "The OpenAI API Key is not sent to Google."
msgstr "OpenAI APIキーはGoogleには送信されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:315
msgid ""
"WordPress user identifiers, cookies, and IP addresses are not included in "
"this GA4 request body by design."
msgstr ""
"このGA4リクエスト本文には、設計上、WordPressユーザー識別子、Cookie、IPアドレ"
"スは含まれません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:322
msgid "Fetch GA4 Data"
msgstr "GA4データを取得"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:327
msgid ""
"Fetch GA4 Data validates the conditions, fetches GA4 preset reports, and "
"creates a Data Preview."
msgstr ""
"「GA4データを取得」では、条件を確認し、GA4のプリセットレポートを取得して送信"
"データのプレビューを作成します。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:354
msgid "You do not have permission to perform this action."
msgstr "この操作を行う権限がありません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:367
msgid "Security check failed. Please reload the page and try again."
msgstr ""
"セキュリティチェックに失敗しました。ページを再読み込みして再試行してくださ"
"い。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:387
msgid "Invalid action."
msgstr "無効な操作です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:601
msgid ""
"The GA4 data could not be converted into valid data for OpenAI. Please check "
"the settings and try again."
msgstr ""
"GA4データをOpenAIへ送信できる形式に変換できませんでした。設定を確認して再試行"
"してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:649
msgid ""
"Google connection needs to be renewed before GA4 data can be fetched. Open "
"Settings, reconnect Google, and try again. Credential values are not "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"GA4データを取得する前にGoogle接続の更新が必要です。設定を開いてGoogleに再接続"
"し、再試行してください。認証情報の値は表示されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:653
msgid ""
"Google connection is not ready for GA4 requests. Open Settings, reconnect "
"Google, and try again. Credential values are not displayed."
msgstr ""
"Google接続はGA4リクエストに使用できる状態ではありません。設定を開いてGoogleに"
"再接続し、再試行してください。認証情報の値は表示されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:656
msgid ""
"Google connection is not configured. Open Settings, configure Google OAuth, "
"connect your Google account, and try again. Credential values are not "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Google接続が設定されていません。設定を開いてGoogle OAuthを設定し、Googleアカ"
"ウントに接続してから再試行してください。認証情報の値は表示されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:676
msgid ""
"The saved report data is missing, expired, or no longer valid. Please fetch "
"GA4 data again."
msgstr ""
"一時保存されたレポートデータが見つからない、期限切れ、または無効です。GA4デー"
"タを再取得してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:730
msgid "Start date is invalid."
msgstr "開始日が無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:734
msgid "End date is invalid."
msgstr "終了日が無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:742
msgid "End date must be the same as or later than start date."
msgstr "終了日は開始日以降の日付にしてください。"

#. translators: %d: maximum report period days.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:756
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The report period cannot exceed %d days. Please choose a shorter date range."
msgstr ""
"レポート期間は%d日を超えることはできません。より短い期間を選択してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:766
msgid "Comparison option is invalid."
msgstr "比較オプションが無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:774
msgid "Data scope is invalid."
msgstr "データ範囲が無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:817
msgid ""
"Comparison period could not be calculated. Please choose a different date "
"range or comparison option."
msgstr ""
"比較期間を計算できませんでした。別の期間または比較オプションを選択してくださ"
"い。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:862
msgid ""
"GA4 data was fetched and the data for OpenAI was prepared with warnings."
msgstr "GA4データを取得し、警告付きでOpenAIへ送信するデータを準備しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:874
msgid ""
"GA4 preset reports were fetched and the data for OpenAI was prepared "
"successfully."
msgstr ""
"GA4のプリセットレポートを取得し、OpenAIへ送信するデータを準備しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:884
msgid "AI report was generated."
msgstr "AIレポートを生成しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:885
msgid "View the generated report draft."
msgstr "生成レポート下書きを見る。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:897
msgid "Please fix the following errors."
msgstr "以下のエラーを修正してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:928
msgid "Validated Conditions"
msgstr "検証済み条件"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:945 includes/class-report-builder.php:1274
msgid "Comparison Period"
msgstr "比較期間"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:952 includes/class-report-builder.php:966
msgid "None"
msgstr "なし"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:961
msgid "Normalized Path"
msgstr "正規化パス"

#. translators: 1: report language name, 2: output locale.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:994
#, php-format
msgid "Report language: %1$s (%2$s)"
msgstr "生成するレポートの言語: %1$s（%2$s）"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1022
msgid "AI Data Preview"
msgstr "AI送信データのプレビュー"

#. translators: %d: number of minutes the report data is saved temporarily.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1028
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The data to be sent to OpenAI has been saved temporarily for %d minutes."
msgstr "OpenAIへ送信するデータを%d分間一時保存しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1035
msgid ""
"The reviewed report data is stored temporarily for this user and expires "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"確認済みのレポートデータはこのユーザー向けに一時保存され、自動的に期限切れに"
"なります。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1051
msgid "Structured pre-send review"
msgstr "送信前の構造化レビュー"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1054
msgid "Review this structured summary before sending data to AI."
msgstr "AIにデータを送信する前に、この構造化された要約を確認してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1058
msgid ""
"This preview focuses on report conditions, data availability, warnings, and "
"generation readiness."
msgstr ""
"このプレビューでは、レポート条件、データの利用可否、警告、生成準備状況を確認"
"できます。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1062
msgid ""
"Use the status and warning information below to decide whether to generate a "
"report."
msgstr "以下の状態と警告情報を確認して、レポートを生成するか判断してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1066
msgid ""
"The reviewed report data can include host name, page path, traffic channel/"
"source, city, summary metrics, and comparison differences."
msgstr ""
"確認済みのレポートデータには、ホスト名、ページパス、トラフィックチャネル/ソー"
