"When entering it manually, paste the value into this field and click Save "
"Settings."
msgstr "手入力する場合は、この入力欄に値を入力して「設定を保存」を押します。"

#: includes/class-settings.php:721 includes/class-settings.php:741
#: includes/class-settings.php:762
